<item>
            <title>[SPARK-46893] Remove inline scripts from UI descriptions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-46893</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Users can inject inline scripts (e.g. &lt;tt&gt;onclick&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;onmouseover&lt;/tt&gt; handlers) in the UI job and stage descriptions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The UI already has precaution to treat, e.g., &lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;script&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt; tags as plain-text. But that doesn&apos;t extend to inline scripts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Bad job descriptions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
scala&amp;gt; sc.setJobDescription(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&quot;&quot;&amp;lt;a href=&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/link&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; onmouseover=&quot;&lt;/span&gt;alert(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;oops&apos;&lt;/span&gt;);&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&amp;gt;onmouseover&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&quot;)

scala&amp;gt; spark.sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SELECT 1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).show()
...

scala&amp;gt; sc.setJobDescription(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&quot;&quot;&amp;lt;a href=&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/link&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; onclick=&quot;&lt;/span&gt;alert(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;oops&apos;&lt;/span&gt;);&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&amp;gt;onclick&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&quot;)

scala&amp;gt; spark.sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SELECT 1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).show()
...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13066306/13066306_Screenshot+2024-01-29+at+09.06.34.png&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
